WEBVTT

00:30.864 --> 00:34.576
There's a perfectly good staircase,
and no one ever uses it.

00:34.659 --> 00:38.455
It's been a while
since you've set foot on this seabed.

00:38.538 --> 00:40.957
The troublemaker of the Great Hall.

00:41.541 --> 00:44.294
That was a long time ago, Alaira.

00:44.377 --> 00:45.920
Was it though?

00:46.671 --> 00:49.424
I hear you've stirred up trouble again.

00:50.633 --> 00:53.511
Word is, you've taken on a new apprentice.

00:53.595 --> 00:55.138
You know already?

00:55.221 --> 00:56.890
Word travels fast.

00:57.390 --> 00:59.559
I mean, they might be tied, right?

01:00.143 --> 01:02.062
To the "Brimmed Caps"?

01:04.272 --> 01:06.941
It's been four years
since forbidden magic was used.

01:07.025 --> 01:08.526
She's an important lead.

01:09.444 --> 01:11.321
That's not why.

01:12.781 --> 01:16.326
She hasn't taken the exam yet,
so she isn't officially my apprentice.

01:16.409 --> 01:18.203
What? Not yet?

01:18.286 --> 01:19.954
It's too soon.

01:20.038 --> 01:21.456
And the timing's bad.

01:22.040 --> 01:23.291
Oh, that's right.

01:23.374 --> 01:26.211
This time of year, the Dadah Range
where exams are held...

01:26.294 --> 01:29.214
Is at its highest elevation.

01:29.297 --> 01:31.716
I can't send her out there now.

01:32.467 --> 01:34.260
Her life would be at risk.

03:19.240 --> 03:20.992
Hey, Agott?

03:22.243 --> 03:25.288
Are we really doing this?
The master isn't even here.

03:25.371 --> 03:26.664
THE TRIAL AT DADAH RANGE

03:26.748 --> 03:28.875
You test alone no matter when you do it.

03:28.958 --> 03:31.794
But I just got here.

03:31.878 --> 03:34.756
I passed when I was ten.

03:34.839 --> 03:37.217
Everyone takes it to become an apprentice.

03:37.300 --> 03:38.635
The conditions never change.

03:39.135 --> 03:40.136
I see.

03:41.554 --> 03:44.432
The first test is the
"Consent of the Crown."

03:44.933 --> 03:48.645
You can only bring
three magical contraptions and materials.

03:48.728 --> 03:52.941
You have to reach the peak
of Dadah Range without anyone's help

03:53.024 --> 03:56.319
and bring back the diadem herb
that grows there.

03:56.903 --> 03:59.864
The guidance orb that shows the way
to any destination,

03:59.948 --> 04:01.824
and the vapor bubble for drinking water.

04:01.908 --> 04:04.827
That's probably all you can manage.

04:06.287 --> 04:08.248
Now go.

04:11.668 --> 04:13.962
Oh, and, um...

04:15.630 --> 04:17.215
Do you have any shoes?

04:17.966 --> 04:20.718
- Shoes?
- Those shoes are contraptions too, right?

04:21.469 --> 04:23.346
I saw the soles glowing

04:23.429 --> 04:25.723
when you and Master Qifrey
were flying around.

04:25.807 --> 04:30.228
So, if you don't mind, those shoes,

04:30.812 --> 04:34.148
maybe you can lend them to me?

04:34.732 --> 04:36.985
That's too much to ask! I'm sorry!

04:37.068 --> 04:38.861
Forget I asked!

04:44.826 --> 04:46.577
I'll lend them to you.

04:47.078 --> 04:49.497
- Just hurry up.
- Thanks...

04:49.580 --> 04:51.541
And go!

04:53.584 --> 04:54.961
I forgot to tell you,

04:55.044 --> 04:57.922
but you can only take the test once.

04:58.006 --> 04:59.424
If you fail,

04:59.507 --> 05:02.635
you can't be approved as
Master Qifrey's apprentice.

05:02.719 --> 05:04.679
You'll have to leave the atelier.

05:15.148 --> 05:17.483
I suddenly feel so alone,

05:18.526 --> 05:20.361
but I've got to do my best!

05:20.445 --> 05:22.363
There's no turning back.

05:23.906 --> 05:27.618
I wonder how you use the guidance orb.

05:38.129 --> 05:40.590
It must be telling me to go this way.

05:43.384 --> 05:44.510
Okay!

05:44.594 --> 05:47.180
It's just hiking. No big deal.

05:51.267 --> 05:52.935
I can do it!

05:53.019 --> 05:56.105
Agott said she passed

05:56.189 --> 05:58.649
when she was ten!

06:01.986 --> 06:04.572
If she did it at ten...

06:08.659 --> 06:11.662
I'm sure it's a piece of cake!

06:19.712 --> 06:20.838
No way.

06:22.632 --> 06:23.591
Don't tell me...

06:31.599 --> 06:34.852
That's Dadah Range?

06:40.066 --> 06:43.194
The guidance orb is pointing up.

06:43.277 --> 06:45.071
So it must be there.

06:49.951 --> 06:52.537
I never thought it'd be floating
in the sky.

06:59.919 --> 07:01.045
Ta-da!

07:01.671 --> 07:03.381
The shoes I borrowed from Agott!

07:03.881 --> 07:05.425
Hup!

07:18.896 --> 07:22.859
The seal is split with half on each foot.

07:30.658 --> 07:32.285
Make sure they don't shift.

07:32.368 --> 07:34.036
Align them perfectly...

07:42.420 --> 07:45.590
Wow! I'm really floating!

07:53.639 --> 07:55.683
It's like Master Qifrey said.

07:56.309 --> 07:58.519
I'm like a newborn foal.

08:02.315 --> 08:03.357
But...

08:07.945 --> 08:09.280
I flew.

08:12.700 --> 08:15.203
If I can fly,
I'll be at the top in no time.

08:16.704 --> 08:17.705
All right!

08:18.206 --> 08:19.624
I'll give it my best!

08:24.212 --> 08:27.840
You'll get used to it soon
and be running around in no time.

08:29.467 --> 08:32.386
I'll get used to it soon...

08:56.035 --> 08:59.038
- Here's the application form. Thanks.
- Of course.

08:59.747 --> 09:02.166
- Totorei, number 12.
- Yes.

09:02.875 --> 09:06.629
If you lived in the Hall,
you wouldn't have to travel for this.

09:06.712 --> 09:08.548
You can bring your apprentice.

09:09.298 --> 09:11.300
The Great Hall is the witches' stronghold.

09:11.384 --> 09:13.803
It has everything you need.

09:13.886 --> 09:17.098
Then I'll just come when I need to.

09:18.140 --> 09:19.559
I've brought it here.

09:19.642 --> 09:20.560
Thanks.

09:21.227 --> 09:23.813
Your disdain for the Great Hall runs deep.

09:24.397 --> 09:26.566
Keep a close eye on your apprentices.

09:27.316 --> 09:28.818
Kids of that age,

09:28.901 --> 09:32.738
you never know what they'll get up to
with no adults around.

09:34.073 --> 09:36.784
Whoa, easy!

09:38.160 --> 09:41.080
My balance has gotten much better.

09:41.664 --> 09:44.000
I think I can go a little higher.

10:25.333 --> 10:26.584
A brushbuddy!

10:26.667 --> 10:28.085
I've never seen one before!

10:41.223 --> 10:43.684
The shoes are all muddy.

10:53.903 --> 10:56.906
Oh no! The seal's rubbed off!

10:57.490 --> 10:58.908
No! Is it because I wiped it?!

10:58.991 --> 11:00.534
Oh no, no, no!

11:00.618 --> 11:02.912
I know! I'll draw over it!

11:05.539 --> 11:08.918
The ink all spilled.

11:14.048 --> 11:15.466
What should I do?

11:17.927 --> 11:19.679
Maybe it's over for me.

11:21.806 --> 11:25.309
Huh? Hey, Agott, have you seen Coco?

11:25.393 --> 11:27.812
It's almost time for dinner.

11:27.895 --> 11:29.980
Coco's not here.

11:30.064 --> 11:32.316
She's at Dadah Range for the test.

11:32.400 --> 11:33.901
What?! Alone?

11:33.984 --> 11:36.237
But she just got here!

11:36.320 --> 11:37.321
You didn't stop her?

11:37.405 --> 11:38.823
Hey, Agott!

11:38.906 --> 11:41.575
You normally take the test
before you come.

11:41.659 --> 11:44.328
That's true, but...

11:45.037 --> 11:47.957
If she can't even pass such a simple test,

11:48.040 --> 11:50.835
she shouldn't be an apprentice.

11:51.502 --> 11:52.545
You know,

11:53.045 --> 11:56.298
I hate people who can't do what I can do.

11:56.382 --> 11:58.634
I gain nothing being with them.

11:59.301 --> 12:02.179
And an outsider at that.

12:03.222 --> 12:06.934
Don't worry.
She'll be back without even trying.

12:07.810 --> 12:12.648
This time of year, the Dadah Range
floats higher than ever.

12:12.732 --> 12:16.277
Not even my sylph shoes can fly that high.

12:16.777 --> 12:19.947
She doesn't even know the rules,
has no sense of danger.

12:21.907 --> 12:25.119
I don't want an outsider like that
in our world.

12:29.039 --> 12:31.375
You're not going to eat, Tetia?

12:33.169 --> 12:34.462
I will,

12:34.545 --> 12:38.090
but I don't know,
I just have this heavy feeling.

12:42.595 --> 12:43.637
Seconds for me.

12:44.138 --> 12:47.349
Am I the only one worried? Sheesh!

12:47.433 --> 12:51.353
Either way,
we can only wait for Master Qifrey.

12:57.401 --> 12:59.570
Up! Go!

12:59.653 --> 13:00.613
Whoa...

13:01.781 --> 13:02.823
Nope!

13:02.907 --> 13:06.035
I tried using the little ink I had left,

13:06.118 --> 13:08.704
but I can't even lift off anymore.

13:10.289 --> 13:12.833
They're so soaked, it just smears.

13:20.424 --> 13:23.594
What if I draw
directly on the soles of my feet?

13:33.604 --> 13:37.942
No, I can't! Drawing magic
directly on the body is forbidden.

13:40.110 --> 13:44.156
I don't know what kind of magic
to use right now.

13:49.286 --> 13:51.622
Agott was right.

14:00.965 --> 14:03.259
Wow!

14:03.759 --> 14:06.262
Anyone can draw magic,

14:06.762 --> 14:09.056
but not everyone can draw it well.

14:09.765 --> 14:14.645
Maybe only people with special talent
can become witches after all.

14:22.653 --> 14:24.530
Everyone has been drawing magic

14:24.613 --> 14:27.116
since they were little.

14:27.825 --> 14:30.077
What could I possibly do?

14:42.965 --> 14:44.008
Here.

14:48.846 --> 14:51.390
That's right. Straight.

14:53.017 --> 14:54.310
Whoops!

14:56.478 --> 14:57.563
Up we go.

14:59.690 --> 15:01.317
Hey! Come here!

15:06.488 --> 15:08.198
Wow.

15:08.282 --> 15:11.160
I had no idea this village
had such a wonderful artisan.

15:13.245 --> 15:14.538
This is magic.

15:19.293 --> 15:20.169
I do.

15:24.715 --> 15:27.593
I have it! My own magic!

15:49.823 --> 15:52.451
If I moisten it a bit in the water...

15:58.123 --> 16:01.251
My cloak that was wet
is now stiff from the dried mud.

16:01.335 --> 16:02.920
I think I can draw with this.

16:29.989 --> 16:33.450
It's normal to be a little unsteady
with a new tool.

16:36.328 --> 16:40.249
Then I'll just change it
to a tool I'm used to.

16:42.042 --> 16:45.713
My fingertips will be able to move freely.

16:47.006 --> 16:48.173
Freely...

16:56.974 --> 16:57.808
Okay.

16:58.684 --> 17:01.812
Good morning, Brushbuddy.
You're not very cautious, are you?

17:03.022 --> 17:05.399
It's not the prettiest seal.

17:05.941 --> 17:07.359
A properly drawn one would have

17:07.443 --> 17:10.571
a sigil in the center
evenly surrounded by signs.

17:11.155 --> 17:15.576
But I also learned that uneven signs
can create too much force.

17:15.659 --> 17:18.829
So I tried making
just one really long one.

17:19.496 --> 17:21.665
I don't know if it'll work though.

17:30.632 --> 17:31.800
You're coming with me?

17:32.885 --> 17:36.055
Okay, then be sure to hang on tight!

17:36.764 --> 17:38.432
I'm going to close the seal!

17:46.732 --> 17:49.359
What? Why?!

17:49.443 --> 17:52.029
Did I get the direction of the sign wrong?

18:25.854 --> 18:26.939
It worked!

18:27.022 --> 18:30.192
I'm flying with my very own magic!

18:30.818 --> 18:32.694
A real flying coat!

18:32.778 --> 18:34.446
It's a dream come true.

18:46.583 --> 18:49.211
The things I learned helping Mom

18:49.294 --> 18:51.255
helped me with my magic.

18:51.755 --> 18:53.090
I never would've imagined.

18:56.176 --> 18:57.928
The diadem herb is up higher.

19:12.151 --> 19:13.485
The diadem herb!

20:13.170 --> 20:14.379
Mom...

20:21.637 --> 20:23.722
Wait for me, Mom!

20:24.973 --> 20:27.059
I'll take responsibility for what I did.

20:27.142 --> 20:28.727
I promise!

20:32.231 --> 20:36.401
What?! So Coco went to Dadah Range
alone to take the test?

20:36.485 --> 20:37.903
Yes! Yes, yes!

20:37.986 --> 20:41.281
It's too dangerous!
We have to stop her now!

20:41.365 --> 20:43.408
But if we stop her, won't she fail?

20:43.492 --> 20:45.911
It's too soon for her
to take the test in any case.

20:46.662 --> 20:50.165
She's not like us who grew up with magic.

20:51.041 --> 20:52.918
If something were to happen to Coco...

20:53.710 --> 20:56.046
It's not only the girl that'll be lost.

20:56.129 --> 20:57.381
All right.

21:03.512 --> 21:04.388
Huh?

21:04.888 --> 21:06.098
- Coco!
- Coco!

21:06.598 --> 21:08.058
Thank goodness!

21:08.141 --> 21:10.686
Coco! You're okay!

21:10.769 --> 21:14.064
We were so worried about you!

21:15.691 --> 21:16.733
Agott!

21:18.318 --> 21:20.696
I got the "Consent of the Crown."

21:24.032 --> 21:26.326
Have I proved myself?

21:36.628 --> 21:37.546
Coco.

21:37.629 --> 21:40.757
Using magic recklessly
without preparation

21:40.841 --> 21:43.802
or basic knowledge is extremely dangerous.

21:44.303 --> 21:45.887
You should already know that.

21:48.724 --> 21:51.435
A single misstep could have been fatal.

21:51.935 --> 21:53.729
Don't ever do this again.

21:54.313 --> 21:56.982
I'm sorry, Master Qifrey.

21:59.151 --> 22:02.988
And besides, there's no need
to brave danger to prove yourself.

22:03.572 --> 22:05.991
You're already my apprentice.

22:20.130 --> 22:21.506
This is...

22:25.844 --> 22:28.263
It's proof you're a witch.

22:28.889 --> 22:30.515
A source of pride,

22:30.599 --> 22:35.604
and a restraint you wear on your head
to keep you from abusing magic.

22:45.822 --> 22:47.616
As long as you wear it,

22:48.116 --> 22:49.743
don't forget its weight.

22:51.453 --> 22:54.956
The witch hat will always
be watching over your magic.

22:57.626 --> 22:59.002
Take good care of it.

23:00.379 --> 23:01.505
I will!

23:02.464 --> 23:04.925
Good. Then shall we head back up?

23:05.008 --> 23:05.926
Yes.

23:10.097 --> 23:12.265
First, dinner!

23:13.100 --> 23:15.060
You should also take a bath.

23:21.691 --> 23:24.486
Subtitle translation by: Emily Noguchi

23:33.412 --> 23:35.163
The seed has sprouted.

23:36.790 --> 23:40.919
EPISODE 4: AN ENCOUNTER IN KALHN
